node.text:
The secret ingredient that's giving this unicorn hummus from @chiefspicemama its delightful rosy pink hue? Toss in a beet while you're blending your ingredients together—and don't forget the ice cubes!
.
RECIPE
Blend 1 can cooked and drained chickpeas, 2 tbsp tahini, 2 tbsp olive oil, salt, large pinch garlic powder, 1-2 cooked beets, juice of 1/2 lemon and 2 ice cubes to help make it creamy. Top with olive oil, cumin and sumac.
